Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult\Ncases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's stage is a villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black shadow\Nbeneath a chandelier!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wealthy Daughter\NMurder Case (Part 1).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsui Reika (24)\NDaughter of Yotsui Group President
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy 24th birthday, Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly thank you\Nall for being here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May both she and the\NYotsui Group continue to prosper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop eating like a pig!\NYou're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! You guys should eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often you see food like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta love that vintage wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, allow me to\Nintroduce our special guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great Mori Kogoro-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get a box to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a crime to waste any!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The modern-day Akechi Kogoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, he helped\Nmy daughter just yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tough little case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tough case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about that, Detective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found Miss Reika's dog,\NBubble-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ichieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. One look\Nfrom those sharp eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is all it takes to make\Na criminal confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young lady\Nwas wise to choose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you brown-nosers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about you, but he seems\Nlike a middle-aged airhead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked forward to today,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not\Nquite what I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goes to show how childish you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Still waters run deep?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing dumb to catch\Nan opponent off guard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a preferred tactic\Nof all great detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She anticipated that very fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention\Nbeautiful and refined!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who won her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno, but he's\Ngonna be one happy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets to be the next\Nhead of the Yotsui Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom... Bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hallway sure is dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't the lights on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shower room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The lights won't turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights in this\Nwashroom don't work;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,use the one across the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's odd. None of the\Nlights around here work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I changed\Nthem all just recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter's car has a flat tire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take you home in my Ferrari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll take you in my Porsche!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about my Benz?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of your\Ncars have flats, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They got my car too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's rental car seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six cars have flat tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The six of you will\Nhave to share cars with--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to be stuffed\Ninto someone else's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying here\Nwith Yone tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come send for me in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll stay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I, too, will spend\Nthe night and protect her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from these young wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. I can rest\Neasy with you on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave her in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools. Her husband was\Nalready decided two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone left?! Then we should go--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! Not until you sober up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Stay a little longer\Nand tell us about your cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we all play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective. I'll drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme your car keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pity. You were\None of my candidate suitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came here to make sure the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between my company and\Nyour old man's goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Mifune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The fewer rivals the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can say goodbye to your deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone. I'm going to change upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but caged birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't survive unless I feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is\Nchirp to soothe your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all members\Nof the same yacht club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to sail around\Nnearby islands in her boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were great times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the accident\Ntwo years ago, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's old news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised never\Nto talk about it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She certainly is taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need her selfish attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't it been a little too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you\Ntake a look in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check the other rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NShe isn't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she left\Nand got lost in the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to\Nsplit up and search the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where on earth did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Nikaido-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, this is no time to be napping--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nikaido! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone probably\Nheld his head in this fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was alive just a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Meaning he was killed just now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by someone near this lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!\NWho would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of someone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The missing Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's still no telling who.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For all we know, she could be dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The phones are out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the killer's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. There's\Nno phone reception out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option now is\Nto use the detective's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Someone could\Ntake it and get the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now my tires are flat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means someone\Nwants to keep us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to wait\Nuntil the cars come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone-{\i1}san{\i0}. Please make us some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mifune! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The john.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get some towels\Nfrom the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's dripping wet from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know this place well, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to come here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find any sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you check up there for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's none up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Here's some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot we hoarded\Nsome five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that sugar still any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what kind of accident\Nhappened at the yacht club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.\NThat's got nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he was killed,\NNikaido-{\i1}san {\i0}said that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s husband\Nwas decided two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have something\Nto do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Looks like\Nwe'll need you to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about this accident of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened during a storm.\NMost unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we landed on a small island\Nand went off on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little did we know\Na storm was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly everyone escaped\Nback onto the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Nikaido and Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island was so small\Nthat the full tide could submerge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us took\Na life raft to rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found them half a\Nday later with life vests on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the person who went to\Nget them was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the drowned body was\Nfound three days later, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter, Yaeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed her life\Nto rescue Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably worth it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your coffee's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, first we need\Nto find Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split into two groups\Nand check the house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since one of us could be the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's make sure\Nno one gets separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! It's safer\Nif we watch each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start once we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm suddenly sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired\Nfrom all that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a nap on this sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaeko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That takes care of the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be in the forest after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power's out.\NDid something happen upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the circuit breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Across from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shut off the power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With us checking the house,\Nthey had nowhere to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they cut the power\Nand escaped out this window!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where'd everyone go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People often get lost in this forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yone-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NWhat are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed you\Nwhen you scurried outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Ran's all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran! Wake up! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone held my head underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you came, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, she's just asleep.\NShe had me scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This would normally\Nwake a person up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there sleeping\Nmedicine in her coffee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Didn't the\Nold man leave this open?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm. How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ran was attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think someone\Ngave her sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably in the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you and\NRan make the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would never--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't attack her--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were in the forest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she was attacked\Njust because she was here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means that these might\Nbe random murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with her when\Nthe power went out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything strange happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a warm breeze,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then the lights went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air conditioner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12:30! That's when\Nthe power went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the air conditioners\Nwere set to go on at 12:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know how\Nthe killer cut the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is someone\Nin this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous\Nto stay in your room alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Mifune! It's past 4:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cars will\Nbe here in three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I can't stay with you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when one of\Nyou might be a killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in my room too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd all be safest together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 7:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is today's\Nweather for the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's with the coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it while\NI was in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would help wake us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I didn't drug it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bathroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll leave a stain if we don't hurry--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.22,0:24:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two murders\Nwere done the exact same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichieda-{\i1}san{\i0} isn't the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune-{\i1}kun{\i0}. You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.78,0:24:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same could be said about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one\Nwho could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wealthy Daughter\NMurder Case (Part 2)."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.91,0:24:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.29,0:24:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wet shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.66,0:24:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is a sharp Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
